Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:24.10,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,HKT48 was created in Hakata in 2012!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:35.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The reason why these girls are active nationwide is because they have fans who support them very hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:45.54,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The idea to earnestly work part-time to repay the fans was designed by HKT48's theater manager, Sasshi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:52.92,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,This unprecedented, super great show started last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:01:01.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The important point is deciding how to best repay the fans with the money they earn from working.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:06.67,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I had the members think of the best way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:09.81,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'd like something that we can do that will repay everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:11.24,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Like a stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:12.30,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,A stand might be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:15.35,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Yeah, like an HKT48 stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.76,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Then how about we turn the seats in the theater into something more extravagant. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:23.20,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,We hand out juice to the fans who come to the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:25.93,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,That's good. It might be delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:29.31,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Hmm, various ideas were suggested, but they were all thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:34.46,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,But the members get on board with Lovetan's nice idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:38.88,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,An umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:44.98,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,According to the staff, there are some fans who head home wet from the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:49.29,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,, so maybe like a spare umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.29,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Ah, that's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:52.18,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Lovetan, 100 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:02:01.49,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,With the money they'll earn from working, they'll make an original umbrella for the fans who head to the theater despite the rain and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:09.58,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,With that, I'll now announce the member who will work part-time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.57,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,That member is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:25.58,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The first person chosen to work part-time is Miyawaki Sakura-kun, who amazingly came in 11th place at this year's AKB48 Senbatsu Sousenkyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.99,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Of course you've never worked part-time before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:32.66,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,For that Sakura-kun, this is where she will earnestly work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.89,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Ramen store!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:41.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You'll work seriously at a ramen store!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:41.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H9520E0&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HFEFEFE&\pos(960,404)}Ramen Store
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:41.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H000000&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HFEFEFE&\pos(952,708)}Earnest Part-Time Job
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.57,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.31,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,HKT48's serious part-time job documentary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:59.39,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,On the last episode, you saw the idol, Miyawaki Sakura, work busily at a store just before it opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.62,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,My arm is in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:04.40,Tahoma (BF),,0,0,0,,{\fs100}Finally {\c&H9620E3&}Tonight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.69,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,We're going to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:14.67,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,We'll see her work earnestly in the store that has turned into a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.67,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- If you don't hurry up, we're not gonna make it in time!
