Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.74,Tahoma (BF),,0,0,0,,{\fs100\c&H9520E0&}Miyawaki's {\c&HFEFEFE&}Surprising {\c&H9520E0&}Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:28.35,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,In a world she has never set foot into, can she accomplish all the things she was tasked with!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.49,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:33.09,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean it's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:41.93,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,{\fs100\c&H7E00D5&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HFEFEFE&\pos(868,262)}HKT Shakariki 48!
