Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:04.91,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The store that Sakura-kun is earnestly working for is Hakata Ikkousha, located inside JR Hakata Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:11.28,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,They're proud of their deliciously-made soup. Look at it? Uwaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.28,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Makes you want to eat it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:22.24,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,On busy days, they serve more than 500 people. It's a really busy, really popular store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:29.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's finally the opening! Before that, she participates in the morning assembly to make her heart one with the other staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.81,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Things like this is important.
