Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:33.18,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,560)}Before Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:41.10,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Since it's the weekend, I think it'll be busy, but let's do our best to serve all the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.10,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.78,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I came here to work part-time. I'm Miyawaki Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:49.42,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,So that I don't stand in the way, I'd like to work hard with everyone to liven up Ikkousha-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.73,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.03,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.66,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take care of me today, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.01,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:02.37,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,My mood is rising.
