Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:07.25,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,These are Sakura-kun's work duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:10.49,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Go to step 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:20.43,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Since she hasn't experienced working part-time, everything is new to her. First, she'll be lectured on the proper way of serving customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.48,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Training her is Matsuno-kun who has a cute smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Here's an example!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.53,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Welcome! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.00,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,This will be your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.18,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please use this for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.36,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.64,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Fa-fa-fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.11,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:46.28,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,First, let's do a simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,One person at number 5, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:48.93,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.25,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'm going to be the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:52.25,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Please come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.02,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:58.18,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please use this basket for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.18,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:04.50,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's going smoothly. Do you know what the most important point of serving the customers is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.44,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,With a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:12.18,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- That's right! Sakura-kun, it's your greatest weapon, your smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:17.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- I wonder if it'll be ok. When I face an actual customer... I'll be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:21.79,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Think of the customers as the people you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.79,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Ah, the person you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:25.06,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Think of them as fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.06,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Right! If you think of them as fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:30.19,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,By receiving the best advice, all your worries went out the window, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:33.23,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You can do it! If it's you, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.82,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,We're going to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:42.84,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1318,564)}Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.84,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Welcome! How would you like Ikkousha's ramen? Welcome! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.49,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,What should I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:02.18,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,488)}Her mind goes blank the same time the store opens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.82,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:03.62,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Like everyone else, if you could say "welcome" and "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:11.09,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Uh oh, she's sinking to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:14.11,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,504)}Shrinks away because of her nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.35,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:25.82,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Idol Miyawaki Sakura's smile that mesmerizes the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.14,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,With a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.14,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- If you have that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.36,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,486)}Before the opening
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:38.63,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She overcame unfamiliar, difficult tasks with that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.93,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:43.67,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I've never done anything like this before, so I'm having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.97,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,From that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:52.70,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1396,505)}Her smile vanishes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:00.92,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Welcome! How would you like Ikkousha's ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:05.06,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,One person at number 6, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:14.73,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's finally time for her to serve her first customer. It's nerve-racking for us viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.07,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- When you see a carry-bag, go to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.80,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.41,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'm nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.41,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- You're feeling nervous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.32,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,One person, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.32,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.60,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Can she do well this time around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.85,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please put your belongings in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:35.22,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.02,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Did she succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:44.57,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You have to say, "Here, please" first. Once you say that, say, "Please put your belongs in the basket." Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:49.97,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.38,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please use the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.38,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.72,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.56,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Yes, over here, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.96,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please use the basket below for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.69,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Yes, over here, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:10.59,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please use the basket below for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.12,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.89,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,498)}20 Minutes Since Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:19.29,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Your seat is over here. Please use the basket for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:20.00,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,498)}Gradually her Nerves Melt Away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.50,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.70,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,502)}Miyawaki Sakura's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:22.57,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.88,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please use the basket for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:29.20,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,502)}Usual Smiles Comes Back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:28.44,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.60,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Your seat is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:36.46,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Like that! Like that! Of course you need to smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:41.09,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun, it's been 20 minutes since the opening. How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:44.06,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Eh? It has been only 20 minutes? It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.06,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's really nerve-racking serving customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:51.26,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,But I'm finally used to the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.44,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:10:00.06,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe this is her first day. There aren't many people who are able to do as much as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:03.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She has guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:07.86,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She has a better smile than anyone else in my staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.93,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you very much! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.93,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:17.20,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Ai, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:20.83,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Did you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.83,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:24.85,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(955,500)}40 Minutes Have Passed Since the Opening
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.85,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.80,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:29.80,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,500)}Now Having the Room to Look Around, She...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.21,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Do you want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.21,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Is that ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:39.95,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,486)}Personally Asks Someone and Helps Out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:38.11,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'll have you wipe it like this. When that gets too wet, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.40,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She has room to spare now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:47.95,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,We were unsure at first, but you should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.63,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- If you don't hurry up, we're not gonna make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.81,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1094,550)}After This,\NHer Smile Disappears Again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.54,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Wah, the store is at its greatest climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.01,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The afternoon rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.98,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,On its busy days, over 500 people come to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:18.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,During peak hours, the number of customers won't slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:24.12,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Naturally, the kitchen becomes a battlefield. There are mountains of plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.72,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sakura-san, Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:33.07,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Um, I want you to help the washing place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.07,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.44,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She moves onto step 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:43.49,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She finally heads to the kitchen. The number of dishes that come in during peak hours aren't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:46.58,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Keep washing, keep washing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.60,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'll do it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:53.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Keep doing the same task.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:59.45,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Keep doing that. And put the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.33,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,In here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:18.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.78,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- If you don't hurry up, we're not gonna make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:28.89,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(965,500)}The Store is Crowded
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.22,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's the busiest time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.71,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:44.20,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,This will never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.97,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The dishes are a bit too piled up. I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.99,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Hmm, stopping the flow of work is the worst thing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:57.78,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,However, watching from here, you're completely a part of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:03.25,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I feel sorry because I'm holding them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.36,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.96,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You're going to start again alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.94,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.94,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:21.38,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you for washing them. Because you're washing them clean, we can make good ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'm happy. Thank you. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:33.02,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You're a really fast learner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.02,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:40.95,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,930)}It's been one hour since she began washing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:56.81,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You made it clean there, so you can take a break. There's a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:56.81,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:02.27,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1264,560)}Break
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.25,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's been four hours since she started working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.98,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Phew, finally a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.49,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:14.43,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I was finally getting used to serving people, but washing the dishes felt endless. The dishes kept coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:19.04,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Working at a ramen store is harder than being an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.47,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,500)}Ramen Meal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.44,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:23.47,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Wah! It looks good. Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.50,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:38.22,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:53.58,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The only thing you're able to say is, "It's good," right? That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:59.31,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's good because you worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:05.20,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(952,500)}Gets Excited Talking About Their Favorite Drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.58,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Ah, a girl's talk? As expected, you're a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:16.52,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1373,562)}End of Break
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.88,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you for the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.96,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.56,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:19.99,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:23.73,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I washed the cups, so can you help me wipe them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.10,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Why did you think about joining HKT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:37.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Eh, I was in the world of show business ever since I was child, and during that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:46.65,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,If I didn't pass the HKT auditions, I was thinking of applying myself more to my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.42,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I wanted to be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.42,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Is that so? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:16:03.13,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,While watching AKB-san, I thought it was lovely being able to make people smile. That's why I auditioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.13,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.71,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Being supported and loved by everyone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Grateful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Honestly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.22,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.42,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:18.42,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:22.92,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'll have you prepare the ingredients now. Take over for the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.33,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Eh? You're going to make a newcomer prepare the ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:31.50,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You'll start preparing the onions for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.76,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You'll cut 7 kilograms worth of onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:38.51,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The way to cut this... Have you ever used a knife before. Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.51,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.39,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Seriously? Seven kilograms of onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.01,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's apparently enough to feed 300 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:47.01,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun, will you be ok? That's impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:51.52,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,All you do is drop this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:59.56,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You want to do it so that there's some texture when you bite into the fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.39,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:05.10,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,If you don't finish in 15 minutes, I'm going to scold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:09.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,1-1-15 minutes?! Manager, I think that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:12.53,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'll try my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.97,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Do your best, at least for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.95,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Ah, what a dangerous way of using your hands. Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.03,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Your fingers are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.59,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Don't cut your hand, ok? It'll bleed and we won't be able to use it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:31.36,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Like you're sliding it. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.39,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Not like you're dropping it, but like you're moving it forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:38.13,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Right, right. Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Ah, that's good! I've seen something like that on cooking shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.97,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Oooh, it won't end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:56.00,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,500)}It's been 20 minutes since she began prepping
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:03.39,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's been 20 minutes since she began the task. The store manager is looking at her with forgiving eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.02,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:05.64,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,But...{\alpha&HFF%}isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.88,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,But...isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:10.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Although you're cutting onions, you're not teary-eyed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:16.47,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The tears aren't coming at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.47,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.92,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's probably, um.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.56,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You normally get teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.28,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:36.29,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'm done. I'm done at three, so I'll be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.29,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.88,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Your trainer, Matsuno-kun, is done with her shift first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:45.87,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun, will you really be ok with Matsuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:51.46,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She's really obedient and when you tell her to do something, she learns it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:57.65,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Her best quality is her smile. She has a really cute smile and her pureness shines through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.38,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She must be loved by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:04.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Huh, but if you had to name her one quality you're not so sure of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:10.59,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Not being able to speak loudly. Of course speaking loudly and being lively are really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:14.58,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Matsuno-kun, thank you! Your guidance was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.50,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,That hat is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It seems like it's going to take a while, so I'm making him help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Ah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's been 30 minutes since she began prepping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:28.00,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It was decided that she wouldn't be able to finish on time alone, so one of the staff members, Nakanosono-kun, will help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.09,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to work part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.53,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Part-time? That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:40.62,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Well, here at Ikkousha, it's lively and energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.62,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Ah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:44.19,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I was drawn to that, so I applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:51.20,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,500)}Asked About His Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:48.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I didn't attend a lot of middle or high school. \N{\fs33}[T/N]: He mumbles at the very end so I can't understand his reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:58.80,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,So I want to do something to help those kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.22,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,That's a really lovely dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.54,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:10.89,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It'll be nice if your lovely dream comes true, Nakanosono-kun. Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.55,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,452)}Six hours have passed since she started working
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:24.30,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Miyawaki-san, you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.30,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You couldn't finish the prepping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:33.61,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Your 6-hour shift at Ikkousha-san is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.41,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,That's why we were able to make something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:42.08,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,He makes fried rice with the onions Sakura-kun chopped up earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:44.09,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,My onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:45.21,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.40,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.78,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,That's good! That's good! That was your brightest smile today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:13.72,Calibri (1080 Shakariki Caption),,0,0,0,,{\pos(1108,528)}After the CM,\Nshe finally receives her payment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:29.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's been 6 hours since she started working. Her shift is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:34.30,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She'll finally receive her long-awaited payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:37.04,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Miyawaki-san, thanks for your hard work. You're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.10,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,This is your wages for today. Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.10,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.76,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:46.05,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She has a lot of guts. That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:53.24,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I thought she might get crushed, especially at the washing area. The washing area is crazy, especially at a ramen store.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:56.73,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She never gave up and did it energetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Sorry for holding you all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.77,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:02.69,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:07.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Thank you for today. You tried your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.36,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.56,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,4,800 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.41,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I earned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:19.89,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:21.89,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:29.46,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's my first time working part-time, and I didn't know just how hard it was going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:34.62,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I've only ever worked as an idol, so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:37.70,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,washing the dishes was the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:44.59,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,When my heart was going to break doing that, my senpais told me that I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:48.98,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,With that, I was able to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:50.98,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,It's really, hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:56.02,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I once again realize how hard it was working part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:01.07,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,She experienced the difficulties of working.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:08.12,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,The happiness and enrichment she was able to obtain there. She capitalized on this experienced and leveled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:12.76,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,You'll be able to meet a new Miyawaki Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:16.19,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,What does working part-time mean to Sakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:22.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,I'm able to grow more than the person I was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:25.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,For me, it's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.34,Arial (1080 Shakariki),,0,0,0,,
